    <title>Women and Girls contributor: Laura Dixon</title>
    <description>Laura Dixon is a British freelance journalist currently based in Bogota, Colombia. She is a former staff reporter for The Times and has written for The Guardian, Monocle magazine, Vice/Munchies and The Atlantic. She currently writes about the peace process in Colombia and how the country is dealing with the legacy of a 50-year war. Follow her @lauradixon, @laurajaynedixon
</description>
